Basically, everything that keeps us safe,

207
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:38,480
working and entertained
comes from electricity.

208
00:19:38,560 --> 00:19:40,840
And more and more of that electricity

209
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:44,000
is coming from solar power plants
like this.

210
00:19:49,640 --> 00:19:56,080
<i>But humans use only a tiny fraction</i>
<i>of all the energy available from the sun.</i>

211
00:19:58,080 --> 00:20:04,840
So, 430 quintillion joules of the sun's
energy fall on the Earth every hour.

212
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:10,040
