00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:37,400
What miracles could we accomplish?

220
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:40,200
What places
could we explore with all that?

221
00:20:44,160 --> 00:20:46,440
<i>According to astrophysicists,</i>

